## Overview

The Blender Toolkit addon provides a WebSocket-based JSON-RPC API for controlling Blender programmatically.

**Key Features:**
- Real-time Blender control via WebSocket
- JSON-RPC 2.0 protocol
- Comprehensive API coverage
- Type-safe commands
- Error reporting
- Security validation

